org: taleas1
app: interio

service: interio-service
provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs16.x 
  stage: dev
  region: eu-central-1
  memorySize: 128

  environment:
    MONGODB_URI: ${env:MONGODB_URI} 

# package:
#   include:
#     - models/**
#     - configurations/**
#     - handlers/**

functions:
  getUser:
    handler: handlers/user/getUserById.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /user/{id}
          method: GET
          cors: true
  createUser:
    handler: handlers/user/createUser.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /user
          method: POST
          cors: true
  deleteUser:
    handler: handlers/user/deleteUser.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /user/{id}
          method: DELETE
          cors: true
  getUserName:
    handler: handlers/user/getUserByName.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /user/search
          method: GET
          cors: true
  updateUser:
    handler: handlers/user/updateUser.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /user/{id}
          method: PUT
          cors: true
  getBusinessById:
    handler: handlers/business/getBusinessById.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /business/{id}
          method: GET
          cors: true
  createBusiness:
    handler: handlers/business/createBusiness.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /business
          method: POST
          cors: true
  deleteBusiness:
    handler: handlers/business/deleteBusiness.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /business/{id}
          method: DELETE
          cors: true
  getBusinessName:
    handler: handlers/business/getBusinessByName.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /business/search
          method: GET
          cors: true
  updateBusiness:
    handler: handlers/business/updateBusiness.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: /business/{id}
          method: PUT
          cors: true
